briefdescription.para: Materialize a weight view into a contiguous buffer (lossless).

detaileddescription.para:
Design goals:
mmap-friendly: map large blobs once, return pointer views
low overhead lookup: sorted tensor table + binary search
lossless: exact reconstruction via mask + exceptions stream

This module intentionally uses a minimal, self-contained JSON scanner that supports the subset of JSON needed for model.dedup.json. This avoids hard dependencies on external JSON libraries and keeps build integration simple.

Mask semantics:
bit=1 indicates an exception element is present and consumed from exceptions stream.
For int4, elements are nibbles in row-major order (index i maps to byte i/2, nibble i%2).
